channel.title: Need Help Via Teamviewer! Will make Co-Owner [317]
channel.description:
I have a 317 server and client. They are set up for me to use.. they are online and the ports are all good, but what I don't understand is that the server won't play on anything except my client made for it unless it's on Moparscape's default ip, 192.0.0.1. That's the only way it works (even then it closes immediately). How do I get it to work on webclients with my No-IP? Need teamviewer help now please!
EDIT: My Teamviewer is ID: 410698004 Password: d52rg1
